items.title: Arizona Craft Brewers Guild names Anderson as agency of record
items.summary:
On the heels of a recent announcement publicizing the addition of three new clients in the first half of 2017, Anderson Advertising & PR announced the signing of one more, in the form of the Arizona Craft Brewers Guild. The group, which serves as an advocate and voice for independent craft brewers in Arizona, made the announcement to its membership earlier this week. “We are beyond excited to be represented by the team at Anderson,”!

The post Arizona Craft Brewers Guild names Anderson as agency of record appeared first on AZ Big Media.
